;
; whisper-mh-block-real-band — REAL openai/whisper-tiny encoder block-0 weights (sliced to
; d_model=12, the real 6-head multi-head, head_dim=2) through the Form tb-mh-block, proven
; against numpy (tanh-gelu convention) within 1e-6. Full d_model=384 runs the same recipe but is
; gated on M5's JIT (literal-emit doesn't scale to ~1.8M-weight programs). Verdict 1 on match.

